[0.044,"o","\u001b[1;36m=== EnterpriseRAG Phase 19 demo: agent-first parallel fan-out ===\u001b[0m\r\nPlanner -> Executor -> Synthesizer agent. RAG is one of its tools.\r\n\r\nThis recording shows AgentQueryPipeline.run_streaming() emitting an SSE\r\nevent timeline for a single 4-way parallel ToolPlan over deterministic\r\nDemoStubPlanner + DemoFakeRetrieveTool fixtures.\r\n\r\nExpected: 1 planner.plan -> 4 tool.span.start -> 4 tool.span.end ->\r\n          1 executor.parallel(fan_out=4) -> 1 synthesizer.final = 11 events\r\nWall-time bound: 450 < elapsed_ms < 700 (4 x 0.5s parallel = ~500ms).\r\n\r\nRun as: APP_MODEL_DIR=/tmp .venv/bin/python -m services.agent._demo_runner\r\nSource: services/agent/_demo_runner.py + services/agent/_demo_stubs.py\r\nSpec:   .planning/phases/19-agent-first-docs-demo-release/19-CONTEXT.md\r\n\r\n\u001b[2m--- begin SSE event stream ---\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
